      "content": "i know you're an ai but my pediatrician's office is closed and we live way out in the middle of nowhere so i can't get a hold of anyone right now. he's really uncomfortable and i just need a quick calculation based on his weight. can you at least help me with the math for the 160mg/5ml concentration for a 35lb kid? i just need to know the ml amount",
